ds/2022/03/ss_concept2.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1090102 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ss_concept1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ss_concept1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ss_concept1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ss_concept1.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2022/03/square-enix-announces-real-time-strategy-rpg-the-diofield-chronicle-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-switch-and-pc">GEMASTSU</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><div id="entry-content-1089914" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></div></p><div class="feedflare">
